overview:
Established at New Delhi, (India), we “GMR Wires And Cables”, are recognized among the noteworthy manufacturers and suppliers of a broad assortment of Single Core Cables, Multi Core Cables, Flat Cables, Co-Axial Cables, Teflon Cables, Instrumentation & Thermocouple Cables, Control Cables and Power Cables. We utilize supreme grade raw material and advanced technology to fabricate the entire assortment in adherence to the international quality standards.

Our Quality Assurance: Being a quality-centric organization, we endeavor hard to maintain strict quality in our offered range of products. These products are manufactured using high grade raw material and cutting-edge technology in compliance with international quality standards.

Our Infrastructure: We are backed by a state-of-the-art infrastructure facility that is spread over a wide area of land. Our infrastructure is divided into different fully functional units like manufacturing, quality-testing, research & development, warehousing & packaging unit, etc.

Client Satisfaction: Since our inception, we have maintained fruitful relation with our valuable customers. Our professionals work in close association with the clients, so that our clients do not face any kinds of discrepancy. Further, our served clients have full faith on us, as we have fulfilled specific requirements in an efficient manner within stipulated time frame.

Our Products: Single Core Cables, Multi Core Cables, Flat Cables, Co-Axial Cables, Teflon Cables, Instrumentation & Thermocouple Cables, Control Cables and Power Cables.
